://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war-warhammer-3"><em>《全面战争：战锤 3》</em></a>扩展包<em>《Shadows Of Change》</em>的预告片展示了三位传奇人物在战略游戏中的力量。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/how-total-war-warhammer-3-carved-out-an-empire-3353623">《全面战争：战锤 3》如何打造一个帝国</a></strong></li></ul><p>这些是奸奇的换生灵、大华夏的玉龙<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-reveals-first-lord-from-shadows-of-change-dlc-3475457">元波</a>和基斯里夫的母亲奥斯坦基亚。看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《全面战争：战锤 III - 变革之影》公布预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ro4KbCpcXZM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>幻形灵并不是场上最强的演员，但是，他能够为这些力量触发扭转局势的机会。<a href="https://www.totalwar.com/blog/tww3_soc_thechangeling/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小计划</a>包括在定居点建立邪教以及建造寄生或共生建筑的能力，为玩家提供一系列优势。</p><p>他麾下的部队包括 Tzaangors、Cockatrice、Mutalith Vortex Beast 和 Blue Scribes，它们“在战场上空翱翔时，随机释放出神秘的死亡爆炸”。</p><p>元博运用巫术和治国之道来播种成功。他的部队有天将、玛瑙鸦人、玉狮和喷射狮。后两者是神奇的，玉狮可以恢复魔法储备并用火焰进行攻击，而喷射狮可以影响敌方法师的准确性并增强友方魔法使用者的能力。</p><p>最后，基斯里夫儿童是在对奥斯坦基亚母亲的恐惧中长大的。作为一名强大的女巫，她寻找禁忌的六角形，玩家可以在《女巫狩猎》中将其组合起来创造新的咒语。她的单位是野兽的元素化身、林中之物、阿克希娜游骑兵和女巫。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480374" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480374" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3480374" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/total-war-warhammer-3-shadows-of-change-DLC-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480374" class="wp-caption-text"> 《全面战争：战锤 3》图片来源：Creative Assembly</figcaption></figure><p>在<em>《Shadows Of Change》8 月 31 日发售之前预订《Shadows Of Change》</em>的玩家将获得全价 10% 的折扣。</p><p>此外，还将免费添加另一位传奇英雄——Aekold Helbrass。 “被追赶到混乱荒原的边缘，并从死亡边缘被拯救，他重生为奸奇冠军，”工作室表示。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two-interactive">Take-Two Interactive</a>为即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/red-dead-redemption"><em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em></a>移植版的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-publisher-defends-re-releases-controversial-price-3480337">价格</a>进行了辩护，粉丝们指出，目前 Xbox 上的移植版价格更便宜。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-warhammer-3-drops-action-packed-trailer-for-shadows-of-change-dlc-3480349">《全面战争：战锤 3》发布的《Shadows Of Change》DLC 动感十足的预告片</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
